videos.headline: UAB's huge pass play to begin game sets up rush TD
videos.description: Bryson Lucero airs it out to Austin Watkins for a 56-yard gain, and Spencer Brown finishes the touchdown drive with a 15-yard run for UAB.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UAB's huge pass play to begin game sets up rush TD) 2020/9/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brown punches in second TD for UAB
videos.description: Spencer Brown's second rushing touchdown of the game caps off a 12-play, 76-yard drive for UAB against South Alabama.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brown punches in second TD for UAB) 2020/9/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: S. Alabama WR 'Mosses' defender, rocks baby to celebrate
videos.description: South Alabama QB Chance Lovertich slings a 38-yard touchdown to Jalen Tolbert, who leaps over the UAB defender for an incredible catch.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (S. Alabama WR 'Mosses' defender, rocks baby to celebrate) 2020/9/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brown sets UAB record with 36th career TD
videos.description: UAB RB Spencer Brown's third touchdown of the game marks the 36th of his career and the most rushing scores in school history.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brown sets UAB record with 36th career TD) 2020/9/24 ESHEET
